examples.en: The burglars left the house in an awful mess.
The burglars robbed him of all his money.
A visible alarm makes burglars think twice.
The burglars fled after triggering the alarm.
The burglars have turned our house upside down.
...the burglars broke in by smashing a window...
The burglars broke in through the kitchen window.
Burglars had been in and turned the whole house over.
The burglars overturned all the furniture in the house.
A security guard surprised the burglars in the storeroom.
He decided to play along with the burglars for the moment.
The burglars gagged the home owner and tied him to a chair.
By the time the police arrived on the scene, the burglars had fled.
I put an extra lock on the door as an added insurance against burglars.
The burglars despoiled the art museum in search of treasures they thought they could sell to a fence.
